(80, 6, 7, 0, 0, 0, 7, 7, 7, 'tidak', '<ul class=\"ul1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Menlo;\"></span>Dijelaskan studi kasus atau diambil dari PT mana (jika tidak diijinkan, nama PT bisa diganti jadi PT. X)</li><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Menlo;\"></span>Tuliskan alur pengajuan cuti dan ketentuan cuti di laporan (sehingga dapat membantu penulisan deskripsi sistem) sehingg dapat menggambarkan latar belakang lebih lengkap</li><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Menlo;\"></span>Batasan masalah diperbaiki, masukkan hal-hal yang tidak ditangani</li><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Menlo;\"></span>Tambahkan penelitian terdahulu lebih banyak, minimal 5 aplikasi yang lain, sehingga dapat memberi gambaran aplikasi yang akan dibangun</li><li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;; color: rgb(69, 69, 69);\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 10px; line-height: normal; font-family: Menlo;\"></span>Ada beberapa kesalahan tulis, harap diperbaiki</li></ul>', '-', 'Disetujui Pembimbing'),
