(162, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 8, 7, 8, 'tidak', '<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">1. Latar belakang kurang menunjukkan alasan dan data-data yang\r\nkuat.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">2. Rumusan masalah dan tujuan diperbaiki lagi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">3. Belum ada perbandingan penelitian terdahulu dengan ide\r\npenelitian anda sekarang. Apakah sama? lebih baik?<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\">4. Landasan teori belum ada data awal yang anda perlukan untuk\r\npenelitian di perusahaan serta alur sistem yang sudah ada.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;\"