(164, 23, 8, 8, 9, 8, 8, 9, 9, 'tidak', '<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Persepsi\r\nmasyarakat yg diinginkan itu apa? Dan masyarakat nya seperti apa? (bagian tujuan )</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nCalibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">apakah hasil dari TA ini sudah mencapai dan sesuai dengan tujuan pada bab 1 nya<br></span><br></p>', 'uploads/tugas_akhir/4311931004/230_laporan_perbaikan_164.pdf', 'Disetujui Penguji'),
