(267, 39, 8, 0, 0, 0, 8, 8, 9, 'tidak', '<p><br></p><p>-apa definisi sampah organik non organik</p><p>-bagaimana bisa di bedakan hanya dari kadar air</p><p>-cek lagi rumusan masalah, batasan masalah</p><p>-cari minimal 5 referensi terkait yang membahas sampah oraganik non organik bukan referensi tong sampah membuka otomatis</p>', '-', 'Belum Perbaikan'),
(269, 20, 7, 0, 0, 0, 7, 7, 8, 'tidak', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Pertajam kembali latar belakang, tujuan juga\r\nrumusan masalah.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Batasan penelitian pastikan sesuai dengan apa\r\nyang ingin dilakukan.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Cek karakteristik sumber data dan karakter\r\ninsteraksi data dengan real world, karena ini terkait pemilihan metode yang\r\ningin dilakukan.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Diagram alir silahkan disesuaikan dengan detail\r\npengerjaan.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if 