(466, 17, 'Implementasi Video Pembelajaran Berbasis Podcast  Pada Materi Etika Profesi Dunia Kerja', 'Information technology makes changes in the education system that gives birth to new features.  Reforms in education are carried out in order to improve the quality of education such as new breakthroughs.  One of them is the use of podcast-based learning video media in learning activities in order to attract attention, thus fostering curiosity and being motivated to learn, by using video media will have an effect on the learning process.  For this reason, this Final Project will implement a podcast-based learning video on professional ethics material.  In this final project, the method used in the process of knowing students\' perceptions of this learning video is a quantitative method using the 4D Model. The results of this final project will be used as a medium for learning professional ethics material for the animation study program at the Batam State Polytechnic.', 'Proposal'),
